tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE voter_feedback (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    voter_id INT,
    feedback TEXT,
    complaint TEXT,
    date_submitted TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE Complaints (
    complaint_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    voter_id INT,
    complaint_text TEXT,
    complaint_date DATE,
    resolved BOOLEAN
);

CREATE TABLE FeedbackHistory (
    feedback_id INT,
    voter_id INT,
    feedback_text TEXT,
    response TEXT,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE complaint (
  complaint_id INT,
  voter_id INT,
  complaint_text TEXT,
  status VARCHAR(50),
  timestamp TIMESTAMP
);
